message.entry: extractFreak expected its first input to be of uint8 type.
extractFreak expected its third input to be a 1-by-1 structure.
Invalid number of fields in the extractor parameters structure.
nbOctave, patternScale fields of parameters structure must be double.
orientationNormalized, scaleNormalized fields of parameters structure must be double.
FREAK parameters structure must have {0} field.
Code generation for FREAK features is not supported.
